{"tid":582032,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人小學/中學個陣比學校逼去參加保良局領袖訓練營","createTime":"2018-03-05T23:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T23:14:03.000Z","uid":120466,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"216e3782f1fca0a304cf8c96458a25faeeedbde7","tid":582032,"uid":120466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T23:33:49.000Z","msg":"話說小弟岩岩食飯個陣睇睇下新聞咁岩見到有個係講 保良局領袖訓練營既新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之後見到 好多變態教練當d細佬仔狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後我突然諗番起自已小6個陣又有參加過d咁既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為個陣學校逼9我去參加冇得say no  <br />\n<br />\n依家諗番起以前d教練點樣操我地真係好撚變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好記得有一次有一班唔知咩活動輸左 要比班教練係到 圍住話垃圾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  （依個印象好深刻）<br />\n<br />\n仲有一次唔記得做咩事 成級人要扮鴨仔行行勁耐 仲要邊行邊講 我係鴨仔 定 我知錯啦 （唔太記得要講咩，類似咁既意思）<br />\n<br />\n同埋個陣有次唔知咩活動達唔到佢既標準，成班要用手拎住磚頭，唔小心跌左要加多一塊磚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  男女都要。個陣有個肥仔唔小心跌左幾次 加左勁多塊磚落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇見都覺難受。 大佬啊 小學生炸，好撚重嫁。仲要唔係拎幾分鐘 好似拎左成半個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  痴撚線。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原本都唔記得左自己有去，睇完新聞咩都記得番晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5705b51fbf8e95d785e1a473b01bb31420cdbe2","tid":582032,"uid":120466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T00:30:21.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"365264013471acfc70a6eba3a81e99a483583c30","tid":582032,"uid":9732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T02:16:43.000Z","msg":"有次排隊俾人刮左巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4795ee63768f930be3a6d091b23f133bea426e02","tid":582032,"uid":132249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T02:21:28.000Z","msg":"又回帶"},{"pid":"5dae5d21eadbfab3df74f631f4a7cbae1e592caa","tid":582032,"uid":42374,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T02:50:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Kenny我屌你老母死全家落地獄啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"b4c79cd1cd4d514a00dbf7e4edffb94d0146e395","tid":582032,"uid":77138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T03:52:58.000Z","msg":"又回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw推班學生去既個班校長俾人告未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5d0ee94fcd4695ea20570ff305a0bacb2cd200","tid":582032,"uid":120466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T16:22:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔可以比依d人 生活得咁開心"},{"pid":"5d414c272c23a27fcfa1761b9f95caf0d4b9ae16","tid":582032,"uid":34277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T17:06:40.000Z","msg":"雖然聲勢無以前咁勁<br />\n但而家每年仲有起碼千幾個學生受害<br />\n大家唔好掉以輕心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"186b3f34dcf7e726f58e841c013e0ff5d4c1b80b","tid":582032,"uid":144522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T19:39:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f77411605a764048c